                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "SDGP6",
                  "name": "premiseText",
                  "fill": "#c4b8d9",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "You inherit a crumbling estate on the edge of a dying town. Something inside the walls has been waiting for you.\n\nThe caretaker knows more than he says. A historian arrives with questions that mirror your own. And the manor itself seems to shift when you're not looking — doors that weren't there before, photographs that change overnight, whispers from beneath the floorboards.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
