          "layoutPosition": "absolute",
          "x": 20,
          "y": 375,
          "name": "Story Prose",
          "width": 350,
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 16,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "1Z5xl",
              "fill": "#E8E3F0",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 350,
              "content": "The alley narrows into a corridor of steam and light. Paper lanterns sway overhead, casting everything in amber. Sora grabs your sleeve and pulls you toward a counter with six stools.",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Playfair Display",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "SmkBP",
              "fill": "#E8E3F0",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 350,
              "content": "\"This is the one,\" she says, sliding onto a stool. \"Three generations. No English menu. Just trust me and point at whatever I point at.\"",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Playfair Display",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal",
              "fontStyle": "italic"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "HMnWR",
              "fill": "#E8E3F0",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 350,
              "content": "The chef nods at Sora like an old friend. She orders in rapid Japanese, glancing at you with a grin that says: you're going to love this.",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Playfair Display",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
